task-rest_bold.json.TaskDescription: Participants underwent a 10 minute, eyes-open, resting acquisition in which they looked at a fixation cross in the middle of the screen.
task-rest_bold.json.Instructions: Participants were instructed to let their minds wander and to not think about anything in particular while they looked at the cross.
